{"tid":1303543,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"比阿媽以為我入左一大。 。","createTime":"2019-07-10T10:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T11:19:52.000Z","uid":180462,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b1fb01fc3a0907426dc2ff7ba0374815bc4c6f","tid":1303543,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"我今年考dse，今日放榜 <br />\n我考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢個仔入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n我心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽講我去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n我起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n我其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為我夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"3a9bdf4dd9e2fb470c6fd1a85aac04c54386157b","tid":1303543,"uid":70463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0061b7d09ee19ec0f9bcb13c4da94b2aa81ec6","tid":1303543,"uid":129348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"回帶系列"},{"pid":"5cb896b7d0aa40f9297aabb1fe2a48be33fb66cf","tid":1303543,"uid":90497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"篇 文 係唔係要開始改一改 以家一大 係科大wo       hku大陸仔學校"},{"pid":"1408a5fd47e328f2e876090ab3dc2755d805582e","tid":1303543,"uid":131717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe58dbebcb63b8abc23c663cd91b1685f4990d8","tid":1303543,"uid":158145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"阿媽誤會左我入左HKU<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同我既情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr